metadata.name: Scrambler 1
metadata.description: The Scrambler Egg is a mystery waiting to be revealed. Stay egg-spertly alert, for nestled within could be a glimpse of potentially new mini JOYs. Rumor has it that top scientists and egg-ceptional egg-titionists at JOYWORLD are attempting to decipher the mystery within. The future, however, remains delightfully uncertain, so keep it safe and wait with anticipation for the moment it cracks open and reveals its secrets!
